social_posts.post_text: Some nights deserve to last forever.⚡️

My heart is soo sad. 💔 I lost my grandfather this morning. Don Hector Cordova had a beautiful spirit and a desire to live life for the beauty that God created it to be, an opportunity to impact others with love and kindness. As a Christian I have peace knowing he is heaven, but in my humanity I wish I could spend more time with him on earth. I am grateful for the blessing of his life and my Abuelo’s profound impact on me. Thank you God for the 89 years of life you gave him on this earth.❤️✝️🙏🏼
How deep is your love? Deeper than any ocean.💘🌊

When you grow up to be a scientist. 👩🏼‍🔬

And your company surprises you with your own Dr. Scientist Barbie 💕
